{{prompt}}

Please respond with a comprehensive branding analysis in the following JSON structure:
{
  "prompt_analysis": "Brief analysis of the branding challenge",
  "strategic_approach": "Your recommended strategic approach",
  "brand_elements": {
    "naming": "Brand name recommendations or analysis",
    "messaging": "Core brand messages and value proposition",
    "tagline": "Memorable tagline options",
    "story": "Brand narrative and storytelling approach",
    "visual_direction": "Visual identity recommendations"
  },
  "target_audience": "Primary audience insights and considerations",
  "implementation": "Practical next steps for implementation",
  "success_metrics": "How to measure branding success"
}
